h6. Steps to reproduce
# attached an image with the issue key in the file name. See REVIEW-17
# try to use that image in a comment, like {noformat}!emw-REVIEW-17.jpg!{noformat}

h6. Expected result
image appears 

h6. Actual result
"Unable to render embedded object: File (emw-REVIEW-17.jpg)

h6. Workaround
(i) As a partial workaround, the user can run a query directly on the DB to disable one module from the _Renderer Component Factories Plugin_, but doing so, the user won't be able to mention links (e.g JRA-32688) on the description and on the comment fields.

# Stop JIRA;
# Login to its database;
# Run the following query:
{code:sql}
INSERT INTO pluginstate VALUES ('com.atlassian.jira.plugin.wiki.renderercomponentfactories:jiraissuelinkrenderer',false);
{code}
# Start up JIRA;

